                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Vincent Auriol, President of France, visited the United States from March 28 to
                    April 4. His meeting with President Truman on March 29 included consideration of
                    Indochina, as did a conversation between Secretary of State Acheson and French
                    Foreign Minister Robert Schuman on March 30. Records of these meetings and other
                    material on the Auriol visit are scheduled for publication in volume IV.</p>
            </div>
